ns-bethe"><i>Swedish Nationalencyklopedin</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.munzinger.de/search/go/document.jsp?id=00000011852">Munzinger Archiv</a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.alsace-histoire.org/netdba/bethe-hans-albrecht-edouard"><i>Nouveau dictionnaire de biographie alsacienne</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://snl.no/Hans_Albrecht_Bethe"><i>Store norske leksikon</i></a>&#160;• <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.vle.lt/Straipsnis/hans-albrecht-bethe"><i>Visuotinė lietuvių enciklopedija</i></a></li>
